OL,3,CMan is missing after 'entering water'
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged altercation on bridge
OL,6,FPolice say a man remains missing after
OL,7,Freportedly entering the River Tyne
OL,8,Ffollowing an altercation.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,11,FRedheugh Bridge in the Gateshead area
OL,12,Fafter receiving reports of the
OL,13,Faltercation shortly before 10pm on
OL,14,FFriday 10 April.
OL,16,FThey say a man is believed to have
OL,17,Fentered the water following the
OL,18,Fincident for reasons yet to be
OL,19,Festablished.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
