PN,42802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776186394
OL,3,CMan is missing after 'entering water'
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged altercation on bridge
OL,6,FNorthumbria Police's Marine Unit
OL,7,Falongside specialist search teams from
OL,8,Fother agencies are carrying out
OL,9,Fextensive searches in the area in an
OL,10,Feffort to locate him but he has not
OL,11,Fyet been found. His next of kin have
OL,12,Fbeen informed and are being supported
OL,13,Fby specialist officers.
OL,15,FA 48-year-old woman has been arrested
OL,16,Fin connection with the incident.
OL,18,FPolice say the investigation remains
OL,19,Fat an early stage and have appealed
OL,20,Ffor witnesses.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
