OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776186394
OL,3,CMan is missing after 'entering water'
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged altercation on bridge
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Andy Miller, of
OL,7,Fthe Force's Major Investigation Team
OL,8,F(MIT), said: "This is an incredibly
OL,9,Ftragic incident where for reasons yet
OL,10,Fto be established, a man has sadly
OL,11,Fentered the water.
OL,13,F"While our investigation is very much
OL,14,Fin its early stages, we're committed
OL,15,Fto understanding the full events of
OL,16,Fyesterday evening.
OL,26,@pD@NOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
