OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776186394
OL,3,CMan is missing after 'entering water'
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged altercation on bridge
OL,6,F"This is an incredibly busy entry
OL,7,Froute to the city centre, and we know
OL,8,Fthere was a lot of activity in the
OL,9,Farea at the time ` including multiple
OL,10,Fvehicles passing.
OL,12,F"We're keen to speak to anyone who may
OL,13,Fhave witnessed or captured the moments
OL,14,Fsurrounding the incident, especially
OL,15,Fthose who may have dashcam footage.
OL,17,F"If you have any information or were
OL,18,Fin the area at the time, please get in
OL,19,Ftouch.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776186394
OL,3,CMan is missing after 'entering water'
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged altercation on bridge
OL,6,F"No matter how insignificant you think
OL,7,Fyour information might be, it could
OL,8,Fprove crucial to our ongoing
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,F"Our search for the man we believe to
OL,12,Fhave entered the water is very much
OL,13,Fongoing and I would like to thank our
OL,14,Fofficers and all partners from other
OL,15,Femergency services who have taken part
OL,16,Fin search activity for their
OL,17,Fassistance."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@LO]
