OL,3,CMan is missing after 'entering water'
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged altercation on bridge
OL,6,FAnyone with any information is urged
OL,7,Fto contact Northumbria Police via
OL,8,Fsocial media, the report form function
OL,9,Fon the website or by calling 101
OL,10,Fquoting reference number NP-20260410-
OL,11,F1079.
